column5: Float tubes and smallies, oh my!!!  Awesome pics Drew!

Reading your reports, I first see the fish, and then the whole entire picture comes into focus, the boat, how the colours behind you have changed and developed, the water clarity or depth , the smile behind your eyes, and then I hear the joy in your words... Such a pleasure your posts are ... a view through your eyes, however small into the spectacular place you call home!  Amazing fishing Drew, thanks for sharing

So... Officially... it’s Autumn at home here in the valley.  Been doing some fishin’.   Day 1.  Mantis Gold.       Day 2.  Mikey's Mesmor"eyesin" Craw-Eyes       Day 3.  Dirty Fallies.       Day 4.  Fish Plan Eh!!!             Day 5.  Autumn Miss-Fires.                     Day 6.  Chunk Thunk Eye!           Day 7.  Backwoods Belly Boatin' Bronze.                   Day 8.  Capper Fatty!     All-in-all the fishing this fall has been one pleasant colorful day after another.
